# 🌍 Azure Language Detector

A simple Python project that uses **Azure Cognitive Services Text Analytics** to detect the language of user-provided text.  

## 🚀 Features
- Detects the primary language of text input  
- Runs interactively until you type `quit`  
- Secure environment variable handling with `.env`  

 
1.Setup Instructions
### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/azure-language-detector.git
cd azure-language-detector


2.Create & activate a virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Mac/Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows

3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt


4.Example Run
Enter some text ("quit" to stop)
Hola, cómo estás?

Language: Spanish
